<p class="has-text-color has-large-font-size" style="color:#403dcc;">Patrol Periods and Times</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"textColor":"foreground-dark"} -->
<p class="has-foreground-dark-color has-text-color"><strong>Ocean Grove Main Beach </strong><br>Saturday 20 Noivember 2019 - Monday 13  April 2020 on weekends and public holidays.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Australian lifeguards will patrol during the weeks from December to February.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>RAAF's Beach</strong><br>Australian Lifeguards will patrol from Boxing Day through to late Jaunary.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

